Like the error message I posted above, I ran into this issue while trying to convert input images from RGB to BGR, and trying to subtract/add the mean pixel value from my input images. I keep running into this error, and jumping between the pip and Github versions of PyTorch show these error messages.

These are the scripts I was using: https://gist.github.com/ProGamerGov/902bd155a5a0f14c2d3bf971eecc7d9b

The model file is this caffemodel (with it's FC Layers stripped): https://style-transfer.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/vgg19.caffemodel, converted to a .t7 model for use with load_lua.
